1–411.
(A) (1) IN THIS SECTION THE FOLLOWING WORDS HAVE THE MEANINGS
INDICATED.
(2) “ENVIRONMENTAL JUSTICE” HAS THE MEANING STATED IN §
1–701 OF THE ENVIRONMENT ARTICLE.
– 16 –

WES MOORE, Governor Ch. 110
(3) “OVERBURDENED COMMUNITY” HAS THE MEANING STATED IN §
